This was my 5th visit to Venice and by far my favorite Hotel in Venice to date.	Out of all the hotels that we stayed in within Italy, this was by far our favorite.	At my first time in Venice, I booked this hotel for me and my mother.	This was a great place to stay in Venice on our honeymoon.	The breakfast was one of the worst we had during our two weeks in Italy.	My husband and I just returned from our trip to Italy and our first stop was Venice.	When I return to Venice this hotel will be top of my list.	We will probably still here again on our next visit to Venice.